_sText:
Note: This is my very first complete map.  It has mainly been made for fun purposes and to teach myself better use of Hammer and overall mapping.

gg_urban
---------
This is a simple gungame map, themed in an urban alley. Only, the inside of the buildings aren't as clean and safe as it might seem...
 
The map contains buyzones and 4 CT & 4 T spawnpoints. It can be started as a gungame map using the server.
The overall is finished, only this was my first attempt at creating a 3d skybox. This might not have worked out optimal :P
